{"arkId":"cl020145826","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl020145826","modified ":"2025-08-20","title":"Portrait de Madame Jean Tronchin, n\u00e9e Anne de Molesnes ( 1684-1767).","titleComplement":null,"denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Portrait de Madame Jean Tronchin, n\u00e9e Anne de Molesnes ( 1684-1767)."}],"displayDateCreated":"1758","currentLocation":"R\u00e9serve des pastels","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1758,"endYear":"","text":null,"type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Liotard, Jean-\u00c9tienne","attributionLevel":"attribution actuelle","linkType":"original","dates":[{"date":"1789","place":"","type":"date 2"},{"date":"1702","place":"","type":"date 1"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q123757"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 38992, Recto","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"vol.30, p.176","type":"R\u00e9f\u00e9rence de l\u0027inventaire manuscrit"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts graphiques","printsDrawingsEntity":"Cabinet des dessins","printsDrawingsCollection":"Fonds des dessins et miniatures","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0.636","displayDimension":"0.636 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0.506","displayDimension":"0.506 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Pastel sur parchemin tendu sur ch\u00e2ssis. Sign\u00e9 et dat\u00e9 en bas \u00e0 droite au pastel rouge : par J. E. Liotard \/ 1758. Annotation vraisemblablement autographe au verso, anciennement sur le carton de protection : Anne Molesnes n\u00e9e \u00e0 Lion le IX aoust 1684 baptis\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u0027Eglise r\u00e9form\u00e9e de St. Romain. Femme de Jean Tronchin ancien Cons.er d\u0027Etat, peinte par\nMr. Jean Etienne Liotard, \u00e0 Geneva au mois d\u0027aoust 1758 \u00e2g\u00e9e de septante quatre ans.\nMesures du cadre: H : 00,92; L : 00,765 et profondeur : 00,095.","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Jean Tronchin (1672-1761), conseiller d\u0027\u00c9tat de la R\u00e9publique de Gen\u00e8ve,puis par descendance dans la collection Tronchin jusqu\u0027\u00e0 Christiane Tronchin, marquise de Hillerin, ch\u00e2teau de Bessinge \u00e0 Cologny, 1948. Acquis par Xavier Givaudan (1867-1966) chez qui il est cit\u00e9 en 1959,Gen\u00e8ve. Andr\u00e9 Givaudan, 1974. L\u00e9on Givaudan, Paris. Vendu par ce dernier \u00e0 Colnaghi, Londres, 1982. Galerie Stair Sainty Matthiesen \u00e0 Londres. Acquis par le mus\u00e9e du Louvre en 1982. Restaur\u00e9 en 2015 en proc\u00e9dant \u00e0 un d\u00e9poussi\u00e9rage de l\u0027arri\u00e8re, en refixant le parchemin sur le ch\u00e2ssis dans les zones de faiblesse, en supprimant les quelques myc\u00e9liums.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Galerie Colnaghi","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1982,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"person":[{"value":"Molesnes, Anne de"},{"value":"Tronchin, Anne"}],"subject":[{"value":"portrait"}],"technic":[{"value":"pastel"},{"value":"v\u00e9lin"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/14\/58\/26\/00\/AGO145826-000_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/14\/58\/26\/00\/AGO145826-000_PE.jpg","copyright":"GrandPalaisRmn (Mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Michel Urtado","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collection